# Runtime dependency closure of the pinned execution-specs checkout used by
# ELEVM's deterministic generators.  Every package is fixed to the version
# observed in the known-good Python 3.11.9 environment; listing the complete
# closure here prevents a later resolver run from silently selecting newer
# transitive packages.  Generate the complete hashed lock with:
#
#   uv pip compile --python 3.11.9 --python-version 3.11.9 --generate-hashes \
#     scripts/oracle/requirements.in --output-file scripts/oracle/requirements.lock
#
# The execution-specs checkout itself is deliberately not a local-path
# requirement.  Generators import it from the manifest-pinned checkout.
